          <h4 class="h4 more">FAQs</h4>
          <div class="w-dropdown" data-delay="0">
            <div class="dropdown-toggle w-dropdown-toggle">
              <div class="w-icon-dropdown-toggle"></div>
              <div>How much do I have to give monthly?</div>
            </div>
            <nav class="dropdown-list w-dropdown-list">
              <p class="paragraph">You can choose how much you want to give from the choices above! $50 a month, $300 a month, or anything in between, you can sleep easy at night knowing every penny is going directly to build a home!</p>
            </nav>
          </div>
          <div></div>
          <div class="w-dropdown" data-delay="0">
            <div class="dropdown-toggle w-dropdown-toggle">
              <div class="w-icon-dropdown-toggle"></div>
              <div>When do we meet the family?</div>
            </div>
            <nav class="dropdown-list w-dropdown-list">
              <p class="paragraph">We'd love to connect you immediately but because we can't have one family wait 12 months due to the urgency of our work we have to wait until you and your friends hit ~$5,000 total. Along the way, you'll get to meet the community your home will be built in and updated on the building process.</p>
            </nav>
          </div>
          <div></div>
