            <div class="dropdown-toggle w-dropdown-toggle">
              <div class="w-icon-dropdown-toggle"></div>
              <div>Is my donation tax deductible?</div>
            </div>
            <nav class="dropdown-list w-dropdown-list">
              <p class="paragraph">Every single cent of it! You'll get a tax receipt each month when your donation processes. (Pro-tip: Ask at the end of the year and we can consolidate into one receipt to make it easier for you &amp; Uncle Sam.)</p>
            </nav>
          </div>
          <div></div>
          <div class="w-dropdown" data-delay="0">
            <div class="dropdown-toggle w-dropdown-toggle">
              <div class="w-icon-dropdown-toggle"></div>
              <div class="text-block-3">Can I trust this charity?</div>
            </div>
            <nav class="dropdown-list w-dropdown-list">
              <p class="paragraph">New Story is not perfect. We're continually learning and evolving our methods, but we can promise we take every donation seriously and work hard to make the biggest impact with it. Luckily, 100% of your donation goes directly to building so you never have to worry if you're really paying for our printer paper with your donation. We've built 800+ homes to date and have impacted more than 3,000 people. Have questions about our model? We're happy to chat about it!&nbsp;</p>
            </nav>
          </div>
